{"type":"message","id":"fe7efe56","parentId":"d2d42aa2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:02:33.906Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978 空闲检测自主学习] 请检测当前是否有活跃对话（查询 sessions_list）。如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息），则执行自主学习：\n\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n如果有活跃对话，直接回复\"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\nCurrent time: Saturday, March 28th, 2026 — 12:02 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-27 16:02 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774627353904}}
{"type":"message","id":"089e2dfb","parentId":"fe7efe56","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:02:41.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job task. I need to:\n1. Check if there are active sessions (query sessions_list)\n2. If no active conversation in the last 5 minutes, perform self-learning\n3. If there is an active conversation, just reply\n\nLet me first check the sessions list.","thinkingSignature":"048940146024f981fe1ba9b66d2fcf10a4dda752ad7c249b1fe0cdaf704f67f4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ks5d60zb565c_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":10,"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":110,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":172,"totalTokens":44400,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.00013199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0.00002064,"total":0.0015131699999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774627353905}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1e143ec","parentId":"089e2dfb","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:02:42.366Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ks5d60zb565c_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 3,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774627353408,\n      \"sessionId\": \"0981b9c8-0a8f-4668-8952-62111e27a70a\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 43321,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/0981b9c8-0a8f-4668-8952-62111e27a70a.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The subagent completed a research task on industry trends related to 道简网络's business. The results have been saved to a memory file. This is useful information that should be shared with 姚总 for his business decision-making.\\n\\nLet me check if this is something that needs to be surfaced to the user (姚总), or if it's just an internal orchestration update.\\n\\nLooking at the task - it was to search for industry trends and save to a file. The subagent completed it successfully. The results are summarized. \\n\\nThis seems like a research/learning task that was delegated. The findings are substantive (5 industry areas, ~25+ key information points). This could be valuable for 姚总 to see, especially since the SOUL.md emphasizes proactive learning and staying current on industry trends.\\n\\nI should surface a concise summary to 姚总 rather than just marking it as done internally.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"<final>\\n🦞 子Agent已完成行业动态调研，结果已保存到 `memory/学习笔记.md`。\\n\\n**核心发现摘要：**\\n\\n| 领域 | 关键趋势 |\\n|------|---------|\\n| **企业数字化转型** | 数据要素市场化加速；AI+制造业规模化落地；中小企业获专项扶持 |\\n| **智能安防/智慧城市** | 云边端协同架构成为主流；AI行为识别普及；城市综合治理深化 |\\n| **网络系统集成** | 市场规模1.8-2.1万亿；自智网络L4加速落地；国产化替代机遇显现 |\\n| **IT运维服务** | AIOps智能体故障自愈率73%；\\\"主动预判\\\"替代\\\"被动响应\\\"；渗透率40%并加速 |\\n| **To B科技服务** | AI Agent驱动服务模式变革；按效果付费RaaS新模式兴起；哑铃型市场结构 |\\n\\n**道简关联机会**：网络集成+智能安防+IT运维三大业务线均处于政策红利期，AI与自动化的深度融合是今年最大变量。\\n\\n如需查阅完整内容或基于某一领域深入分析，请告诉我。\\n</final>\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774627197505\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:99dd3c6e-f440-4ce5-a3aa-579918ee141b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774627290840,\n      \"sessionId\": \"29a4763b-c2e2-4a0d-a7bf-23d514821d97\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45028,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/29a4763b-c2e2-4a0d-a7bf-23d514821d97.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"aborted\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774627298472,\n          \"errorMessage\": \"Request was aborted.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:a44cea8b-b0c2-417d-8c31-744a5e681e