阅\n- 附带道简网络关联分析和关键机会点提炼\n- 适合姚总经营决策参考使用"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774627188196}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774627362362}}
{"type":"message","id":"7eabe92b","parentId":"c1e143ec","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:03:05.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the sessions list:\n1. The cron job session (idle detection) - this is the current cron job itself, not a user conversation\n2. A \"服务状态巡检\" cron session - also a cron job\n3. A feishu subagent session - this appears to be a sub-agent that completed some work\n\nThe timestamps show:\n- Cron session: updatedAt 1774627353408 (about 5 seconds ago from current time 1774627357xxx)\n- The feishu subagent session: updatedAt 1774627195918 (about 2.5 minutes ago)\n\nWait, let me check the current time vs these timestamps. Current time is 2026-03-27T16:02 UTC = 1774627320 in unix timestamp (roughly).\n\n1774627353408 ms = 1774627353.408 seconds - this is about 33 seconds from 1774627320\n1774627290840 ms = 1774627290.840 seconds - about 5.5 minutes ago\n1774627195918 ms = 1774627195.918 seconds - about 2 minutes ago\n\nSo the feishu subagent was active about 2 minutes ago. The question is whether this counts as \"active conversation\".\n\nLooking at the sessions:\n- The feishu subagent session has messages and was active at 1774627195918 (2 minutes ago)\n- The current cron job is running now\n\nThe criteria is \"最近5分钟内的用户消息\" - user messages in the last 5 minutes. \n\nThe sessions shown are mostly cron jobs and subagents, not direct user conversations. The feishu subagent session completed about 2 minutes ago, but that was a subagent task, not a direct user message to the main assistant.\n\nThere's no evidence of a user actively chatting with the main session in the last 5 minutes. These are all background tasks and subagents. I should perform the self-learning task as instructed.\n\nWait, let me reconsider. The cron job is \"空闲检测自主学习\" (idle detection self-learning). The current session showing is the cron job itself. These other sessions (cron:服务状态巡检 and feishu subagent) are different sessions.\n\nThe question is whether there are any active user conversations. The feishu subagent session was active ~2 minutes ago, but that's a subagent completing a task, not a user conversation with the main agent.\n\nI should proceed with the self-learning task since there's no clear active user conversation in the last 5 minutes.\n\nActually, let me be more careful. The instructions say \"查询 sessions_list\" to check for active conversations. The sessions returned include cron jobs and subagents, not user conversations. The feishu subagent was active but that's a background task.\n\nGiven that there's no direct user conversation in the last 5 minutes, I should execute the self-learning task.","thinkingSignature":"f8fd12486b94e4f97db0e26c55dbbbb03606098051402bf497404ccf4c7652d3"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到以下活跃会话：\n- Cron会话（当前任务本身）\n- 服务状态巡检Cron会话\n- feishu子Agent会话（2分钟前完成，已结束）\n\n这些都是后台任务/子Agent会话，**没有最近5分钟内的用户直接对话**。执行自主学习任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_35svbt5p0qoe_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2230,"output":709,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46920,"cost":{"input":0.000669,"output":0.0008508,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00283923}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774627362365}}
{"type":"message","id":"f28f2ed8","parentId":"7eabe92b","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:03:05.852Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_35svbt5p0qoe_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774627385849}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d940082","parentId":"f28f2ed8","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:03:12.762Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to search for industry trends related to 道简网络's business areas:\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\nLet me search for each of these areas.","thinkingSignature":"d182c98dc33ddd07334303a5302d676a0b5efac47bb11cf954eec8de02de1404"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7xwnxh7milim_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年最新政策动态\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\"","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7xwnxh7milim_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 智慧城市 2026年发展趋势\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\"","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7xwnxh7milim_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维 2026年行业动态\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\"","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7xwnxh7milim_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"To B科技服务 企业级市场 2026年最新动态\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3454,"output":297,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47732,"cost":{"input":0.0010362,"output":0.0003564,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00271203}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774627385852}}
